org.cyclops.cyclopscore.tileentity

Class TileEntityNBTStorage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cyclops.cyclopscore.tileentity.TileEntityNBTStorage

  • public final class TileEntityNBTStorage
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a temporary storage for NBT data when CyclopsTileEntitys are destroyed. In the dropped blocks method this tag should then be used to add to the dropped blockState.
